    <debateBody><debateSection name="writtenAnswer" eId="dbsect_503">
          <heading>EU Bodies<recordedTime time="2026-04-21T00:32:00+01:00"/></heading>
          <question by="#PatTheCopeGallagher" to="#Agriculture" eId="pq_647">
            <p eId="para_5611">647. <b>Deputy Pat the Cope Gallagher</b> asked the <b>Minister for Agriculture, Food and the Marine</b> if his attention has been drawn to a matter (details supplied); and if he has had discussions with this office regarding same. [28300/26]</p>
          </question>
          <speech by="#MartinHeydon" as="#Minister_for_Agriculture,_Food_and_the_Marine" eId="spk_886">
            <from>Minister for Agriculture, Food and the Marine<recordedTime time="2026-04-21T00:32:00+01:00"/></from>
            <p eId="para_5612">I can advise the Deputy that there has been no contact with my Department regarding this matter. I would expect that my Department would be formally consulted if such a matter were to be under active consideration. </p>
          </speech>
